          "page_size"
        ],
        "title": "AuditSearchResponse",
        "description": "Wrapped list response. Mirrors the slice 3 list response convention\n(TierConfigList, ThresholdRegisterList) plus pagination cursor and\ntotal_count for the unwrapped underlying query."
      },
